OBJECTREAD: Read an object's history

Syntax: objectread [at <target>]
        psi object read [at <target>]

DESCRIPTION:
  Sense the history and last user of an object. Costs 6 ISP. Range: touch.

  Examples:
    objectread at sword
    psi object read at datapad

NOTES:
  You must know object read and have enough ISP.
  In combat, using psionics costs one attack from your APM pool.

SEE ALSO: psi, psionics, examine
